title: can't see my club tags
body: Hi i can't see my 2 club tags and club chats anymore. Clubs name's are Dogefanclub1337 tag DFC17 and the other one is Full Feeder Team tag 20FFT

replies.body: Hey there, clubs are currently going through maintenance so you may some issues until it's complete.  Check our [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page for updates!  Let me know if the issue persists after the maintenance, and I'll take a look for you directly.
